            <title>[HADOOP-17999] No-op implementation of setWriteChecksum and setVerifyChecksum in ViewFileSystem</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HADOOP-17999</link>
                <project id="12310240" key="HADOOP">Hadoop Common</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently&#160;setVerifyChecksum and&#160;setWriteChecksum initializes all target file systems which causes delay in hadoop shell copy commands such as get, put, copyFromLocal etc.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This also eventually causes OOM.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
